# {{PARENT_NAME}} multi-project AI entry

This directory is a lightweight SpecForge parent, not the default code repository.

For any task:

1. Read `.specforge.json`.
2. Select the target child project from `projects[]` by the user's request and the files being edited. If ambiguous, ask which child project to use.
3. In the selected child project, read `.ai-spec/business/quick-ref.md` first. Read `.ai-spec/AI-START.md` only when quick-ref is not `GENERATED`, or for onboarding, initialization, or a full audit.
4. Treat the child project's `.ai-spec/` as the rule source of truth.

Git and remote submission default to the selected child repository only. Do not commit or push the parent `.specforge.json` or parent entry files unless the user separately confirms parent submission.

Respond in Simplified Chinese by default.
